Layer 26 is divided into 6 sides of 26 numbers each. The 75th position falls on side 2 (positions 53 to 78), specifically the 23rd position on that side. Side 2 corresponds to movement westward along r = -26, with q decreasing from 25 to 0. For the 23rd position, the coordinates are (q=3, r=-26).

The six neighbors in the hexagonal grid are at:
